page.title: 07Family Life
page.content: My name is Dinh Ho.There are seven other people in my family.They are,my mum,my dad,my two sisters and my three brothers.I am the youngest in my family.My{mum makes earrings and we help her. {My dad works in Northern Ireland,in Belfast.He works at the Four Seas Restaurant.My big brother goes to Millfield school in Somerset and he is 20 years old. My other two brothers Khanh and Huy are still in the High School.Hue,my big sister goes to college to learn to cook and my little sister Nghi is still in this school. {My hobby is playing with computers.I have two,a Lynx and a Spectrum.I have also two banks and a building siciety.
